transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hi sir, very good morning, kaise hain aap?
Executive: Theek hai ji.
Customer: Subhash ji se baat ho rahi hai?
Customer: Bolie, bolie.
Executive: Sorry?
Customer: Haa ji.
Executive: Sir Subhash sir ji se baat ho rahi hai?
Customer: Haan bolie na aap kya kaam hai aapko?
Executive: Sir IndiaMART se baat kar rahi thi main, aapka ek catalog hai na safed marble murti kala ke naam se.
Customer: Ji.
Executive: Right, main actually Kunal ki manager baat kar rahi thi, already aapke sath discussion hua tha Kunal ke sath aapke catalog se related, right?
Customer: Hello?
Customer: Haan bolie.
Executive: Sir aap free nahi hai kya? Agar aap free nahi hai to aap mujhe please ek suitable time bata dijiye taki hum proper discussion kar paye waha pe.
Customer: Abhi hum 1 baje ke something free hounga ji main.
Executive: 1 baje ke something na?
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Main aapko 12:30 baje, 1 baje tak coordinate karti hu, aap please ek bar call answer karke 2 minute aapse mera mere ko discussion karna hai, to ek bar discuss kar lete hai sir, theek hai?
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai, theek hai.
